# Venture Foundry Engine: Complete Blueprint

## Executive Summary

The Venture Foundry Engine is a **gamified, Web3-native platform** that transforms abstract ideas (software, music, art, hardware) into revenue-generating assets through collaborative quest completion. Contributors earn **real equity + royalties**, creators get **instant marketplaces**, and you build a **self-sustaining economy** without traditional hiring friction.

**Core Innovation**: Every completed quest automatically becomes a shoppable product with perpetual contributor royalties, creating a flywheel: Ideas â†’ Quests â†’ Products â†’ Revenue â†’ Contributor Loyalty â†’ More Quests.

---

## 1. THE SITE (User Experience Layer)

### Homepage / Portal Entry
- **Hero**: "Turn Any Idea Into Equity" (quest board preview)
- **CTA Buttons**: "Browse Quests" | "Post a Quest" | "View Marketplace"
- **Social Proof**: Recent completions, top contributors, total platform revenue (all on-chain, trustworthy)
- **Navigation**: Quest Board | Marketplace | My Equity | Leaderboards | Earn | Community

### Quest Board (`apps/quest-board`)
**Master Quest View**
- Large card: "Synthwave Production Suite" (Master Quest title)
- Visual progress bar (30% â†’ 3/10 sub-quests complete)
- Metric cards (6 Codex scores): Trueness 0.999 âœ… | Flow 0.60 âœ… | PCS 0.765 âœ… | RPS 0.723 âœ… | CU 0.510 âœ… | Tap10 0.810 (info only)
- Sub-quests grid (collapsible):
  - "Record Bass" (Bronze, $500 ECOS, 0.5% equity, claimed by @musicdev, 80% done)
  - "Mix Vocals" (Silver, $300 ECOS, 0.3% equity, OPEN)
  - "Master & Distribution" (Gold, $200 ECOS, 0.2% equity, OPEN)
- Team roster: Avatar pills with roles + contribution %
- Chat: Collapsible thread for async collaboration
- "Claim This Sub-Quest" button â†’ confirms wallet â†’ locks slot instantly

**Quest Discovery Feed**
- Filter by: Difficulty (Bronze/Silver/Gold), Domain (Code/Music/Art/Hardware), Reward Type (Token/Equity/Revenue), Time to Complete, Reputation Requirement
- Sort by: Most Popular, Highest Equity, Fastest Payout, Expiring Soon
- Infinite scroll with live status updates (realtime via WebSocket)

### Marketplace (`apps/marketplace`)
**Product Grid**
- Each product is a completed quest's output:
  - Thumbnail + title ("Synthwave Album - Vol 1")
  - "From Quest #47 | 4 Contributors | Total Sales: $2,340"
  - Price, buy button (Stripe/wallet)
  - Contributor bios with equity % ("Producer: 60% | Engineer: 30% | Artist: 10%")
  - Demo/preview link, reviews from buyers
- Product types auto-tagged: #SaaS, #Music, #3DAsset, #Hardware, #Course, #Code
- "Buy as Bundle" option (e.g., "Get Solar SaaS + FoamHomes Kit for 20% off")
- Affiliate leaderboard (right sidebar): Top 3 quest products by week

**Product Detail Page**
- Immersive hero section (video demo for SaaS, music player for tracks, 3D model viewer for assets)
- Specs / Features list (pulled from Milestone acceptance criteria)
- Contributor breakdown: Interactive chart showing equity splits, daily earnings streamed live
- Buy section: Pricing options (one-time, subscription, PAYG), payment methods
- Changelog (tied to merged PRs in the quest)
- Reviews + Q&A from community

### Contributor Dashboard (`apps/dashboard`)
**Profile Section**
- Avatar, name, social links (GitHub, Twitter, portfolio)
- "Founding Member" badge (if early), reputation score, leaderboard rank
- Bio: Auto-generated from quest completions ("3D Artist | 5 quests | $4.2K earned")

**Portfolio Tab**
- **Equity Holdings**: Table of all active quests with equity %, vesting schedule, current value (if tracked)
  - "Quest #12: ThoriumOS Core | 0.75% | Vesting 4yr cliff 1yr | Est. Value: $2,400" (assuming $320K valuation from Series A signals)
  - **Key insight**: Show realized vs. unrealized equity; if a quest's underlying startup raises funding, auto-update valuation

**Earnings Tab**
- **Live Royalty Stream**: "Your code earned $84.20 this week" (realtime, updating via WebSocket)
  - Breakdown by product: "Synthwave Album: +$42 (15 sales) | Solar SaaS: +$25 (5 seats) | VST Plugin: +$17.20 (12 downloads)"
  - Graph: 30-day earnings trend, burndown to next payout (weekly, on-chain)
  - Payout history (timestamp, amount, tx hash for transparency)

**Active Quests Tab**
- Cards for each in-progress quest (Master Quest title, current sub-quest, % complete)
- "Time to Completion" estimate based on contributor velocity
- Link to quest board for updates + team chat

**Leaderboard**
- Global: Top 10 by total equity, top 10 by weekly earnings, top 10 by contribution count
- Seasonal: "Q1 2026 Top Contributors", "Fastest Completion", "Best Code Quality"
- Badges unlock: "Polymath" (5+ domains), "Speedrunner" (sub 2-week average), "Trusted" (L20 reputation)

