```

### Phase 1: Foundation (Weeks 1-4)

**Week 1: Quest Board Infrastructure**
- Scaffold `apps/quest-board` with Next.js (Vercel deployment)
- Build UI components: Quest card, progress bar, sub-quest grid, claim button
- Connect Prisma to read `Project` (Master Quests) and `Milestone` (Sub-Quests)
- Integrate GitHub OAuth login + wallet connect (use `wallet-service` package)
- Test locally with 3 seed quests from your 13 startups

**Week 2: Codex Engine Integration**
- Expose `codex_engine.py` as FastAPI microservice (Python endpoint at `/api/score`)
- Input: Quest description, team size, market estimate â†’ Output: 6 metric scores + GO/NO-GO
- Wire quest creation form to call endpoint on submit
- Display 6 gauge cards in quest card UI
- Implement: If NO-GO, suggest 3 sub-quests to de-risk (e.g., "Market Validation Sprint", "Proof of Concept")

**Week 3: Smart Contract & DevRoyalty**
- Write `packages/smart-contracts/DevRoyalty.sol`:
  ```solidity
  contract DevRoyalty {
    function mintDevRoyalty(
      address contributor,
      uint256 questId,
      uint256 equityBasisPoints,    // 100 = 1%
      uint256 ecoTokens
    ) external onlyGitHubApp {
      // Mint ECOS tokens immediately
      ecoToken.mint(contributor, ecoTokens);
      
      // Record equity vesting (4yr, 1yr cliff)
      equityRecord[questId][contributor] = VestingEntry({
        totalBasisPoints: equityBasisPoints,
        cliffEnd: now + 1 years,
        vestingEnd: now + 4 years,
        claimedBasisPoints: 0
      });
      
      emit DevRoyaltyMinted(contributor, questId, equityBasisPoints, ecoTokens);
    }
  }
  ```
- Deploy to Polygon Mumbai (testnet) for initial testing
- Wire GitHub App to call contract on PR merge (HTTP webhook â†’ backend job â†’ contract call)
- Test with 3 internal PRs

**Week 4: Marketplace MVP**
- Build `apps/marketplace` with product grid
- Add Stripe payment integration (handle recurring + one-time)
- Connect `billing-engine` to split revenue on purchase:
  - 60% contributors, 15% platform, 15% founder, 10% reinvest
  - Store splits in Prisma `RevenueAllocation` table
  - Queue Stripe payouts (async job, weekly)
- Seed marketplace with 5 products from your history (upload manually to IPFS)
- Test end-to-end: Buy product â†’ smart contract emits event â†’ contributor dashboard updates

### Phase 2: Alpha Launch (Weeks 5-8)

**Week 5: Onboarding & First 50 Devs**
- Finalize quest board UX (notifications, team chat, real-time updates)
- Launch "Founding 50" campaign: Offer 1.5x royalty multiplier + cosmetic NFT badge
- Recruit from: GitHub contributors to your repos, Splice platform (music), ArtStation (art), Upwork (generalists)
- Seed 10 open quests (5 code, 2 music, 2 art, 1 hardware sketch)
- Send email: "Join Venture Foundry. Build. Get equity. Earn royalties."

**Week 6: Cross-Domain Fusion Quest**
- Launch hybrid quest: "Bioreactor Visualization Game" (needs coder + 3D artist + sound designer)
- Track: Do different domains collaborate? UI friction?
- Outcome metrics: Team formation time, commit velocity, quality of integration
- If successful: Celebrate + highlight on home page

**Week 7: Royalty Stream Go-Live**
- First 5 quests complete â†’ auto-list on marketplace
- Day 1 of sales: Dashboard shows "$X earned this week"
- Leaderboard updates: Top 10 earners, top 10 equity holders
- Bonus: 2x ECOS multiplier for week's top contributor (gamification)
- Community email: "100 PRs merged. $2K in sales. First royalties streaming."

**Week 8: Snapshot Voting (DAO Lite)**
- Enable Snapshot governance: Contributors vote on seasonal quest budgets, fee adjustments
- Voting power = cumulative equity stake
- Sample votes: "Should platform fee increase from 15% to 17%?" (requires majority approval)
- Participation reward: 50 bonus ECOS for voters

### Phase 3: Scale (Weeks 9-12)

**Week 9: Partner Portal & Showroom**
- Add `apps/partner-portal` for hardware/manufacturing partners
- Sync Digital Twin data (RegenCity performance metrics) to partner dashboard
- Real-time leaderboard: "Top 3 partners by device uptime"
- Warrant vesting triggers: "LED fixture sales hit $50K â†’ 10% warrant vest"

**Week 10: Product Expansion & Affiliate Boosts**
- 30+ products live on marketplace
- Introduce "Quest Bundles": Buy Solar SaaS + FoamHomes CAD files for 20% off
- Affiliate leaderboard: Top 3 products per week get featured homepage slot
- Bonus royalty multiplier (1.25x) for featured products

**Week 11-12: Infinite Squad & Seasonality**
- Implement cross-quest talent matching: "Frontend dev from Quest #12 â†’ recommended for UI role on Quest #45"
- Launch "Season 1: Light" (Q1 2026)
  - Themed quests (all related to lighting, IoT, solar)
  - Seasonal leaderboard + unique NFT reward (cosmetic)
  - 10% bonus ECOS multiplier for seasonal quest completions
- Announce "Season 2: Water" (Q2 2026) roadmap

### CI/CD & DevOps

**Local Development**
```bash
git clone https://github.com/yourname/ecosystem-monorepo.git
cd ecosystem-monorepo
npm install
nx run quest-board:dev           # Port 3000
nx run marketplace:dev           # Port 3001
